release.notes:
Limited-edition deluxe 2-LP gatefold jacket with lyrics
Includes Out in the Storm - Demos bonus LP on cloud white vinyl + 12" x 24" poster insert
Includes a download code for both the album and the demos.
Mailorders from Merge came with postcard and an additional 4-panel poster.

℗ & © 2017 Merge Records

Tracked at Miner Street Recordings in Philadelphia, PA
Mixed at Water Music Recording Studios in Hoboken, NJ
